abstract: Intel reported solid third quarter results, while cautioning that worsening economic conditions could have an unpredictable effect on the coming month.
snippet: Intel reported solid third quarter results, while cautioning that worsening economic conditions could have an unpredictable effect on the coming month.
lead_paragraph: Intel, the world’s largest producer of semiconductors, reported a strong third-quarter profit Tuesday but cautioned that the global economic downturn could hurt its business in the coming months.

headline.main: Profit Rises, but Intel Chief Offers a Gloomy Outlook
headline.print_headline: Profit Rises, but Intel Chief Offers a Gloomy Outlook
